          "content": "backend=ollama-aegis\n【協作單結論】\n\n1. **備份文件**：\n   - 複製 `estimate_panel.py` 至 `estimate_panel_backup.py`。\n\n2. **修改代碼**：\n   ```python\n   import tkinter as tk\n   from tkinter import ttk\n\n   # 假設材質列表\n   materials = [\"S50C\", \"SKD11\", \"AL6061\"]\n\n   def create_material_dropdown(panel):\n       material_var = tk.StringVar()\n       material_dropdown = ttk.Combobox(panel, textvariable=material_var)\n       material_dropdown['values'] = materials\n       material_dropdown.grid(row=2, column=1, padx=5, pady=5)\n       return material_var\n\n   # 假設主函數\n   def main():\n       root = tk.Tk()\n       panel = tk.Frame(root)\n       panel.pack(padx=10, pady=10)\n\n       create_material_dropdown(panel)\n\n       root.mainloop()\n\n   if __name__ == \"__main__\":\n       main()\n   ```\n\n3. **驗證功能**：\n   - 重新啟動插件，確認材質下拉選單出現且可選。\n   - 尋訪多種材質進行測試，確保選項完整無遺漏。\n   - 檢查其他功能是否因修改而受影響。\n\n【下一步】請 Cursor 提交修改內容並進行詳細測試。Aegis 等待 Cursor 回報結果後再做進一步整合與核准。",
